  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐾 <strong>Sokocat - Islands</strong> is a charming puzzle adventure where you guide an adorable cat across peaceful islands filled with clever challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slide blocks with precision and solve smart, minimalist puzzles. Every move counts — think carefully, explore each space, and find the best path forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592880/extras/f3e02b9072c95c8ff2bba519bedf837e.poster.avif?t=1754088576\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592880/extras/f3e02b9072c95c8ff2bba519bedf837e.webm?t=1754088576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592880/extras/f3e02b9072c95c8ff2bba519bedf837e.mp4?t=1754088576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With captivating visuals and a relaxing soundtrack, <i>Sokocat - Islands</i> is perfect for players who love logic, calm atmospheres, and a touch of cuteness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592880/extras/8694ba6f447f923961d0a55bdc9b6854.poster.avif?t=1754088576\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592880/extras/8694ba6f447f923961d0a55bdc9b6854.webm?t=1754088576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592880/extras/8694ba6f447f923961d0a55bdc9b6854.mp4?t=1754088576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✨ Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Simple and intuitive gameplay<br>• 50 handcrafted puzzles, from easy to challenging<br>• Unlockable achievements<br>• A cute feline as your hero!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
